# Signing Shortcutst

Apple has an internal algorithm to "sign" Shortcuts since iOS 15 and macOS 12 that is required in order to share/import them into the app and run them on iOS, iPadOS or macOS.

The Cherri compiler uses the macOS binary `shortcuts`, specifically it's `sign` subcommand.

